<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="hero-unit span7 offset1" style="height: 600px;">
    <h1>Jotting Journal</h1>
    <h2 style="padding-left: 35px;">Your journal, everywhere.</h2>
    <br />
    <p>
      It's your life. You should be able to journal it anywhere. That's what Jotting Journal is for. Where ever you are, we're there to help you record what's happening.
    </p>
    <p>
      Anywhere you have a web browser, you can log into your journal, record what's going on, upload a picture, and attach your location.
    </p>
    <p>It's all about context. <strong>Your</strong> context.</p>
    <br />
    <div class="pagination-centered">
      <h2>Try it Free for 30 Days! <small>($36/year after that)</small></h2>
      <%= link_to 'Sign Up Now', new_user_registration_path, :class => "btn btn-large btn-block btn-inverse" %>
    </div>
    <div class="pagination-centered muted" style="padding-top: 12px;">
        <strong>Don't panic</strong>. Mobile apps are in the works.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="span3" style="padding-top: 200px;">
    <%= form_for "user", :url => user_session_path do |f| %>
      <h2>Sign In</h2>
      <%= f.text_field :email, :placeholder => 'email address' %>
      <%= f.password_field :password, :placeholder => "password" %><br />
      <%= f.submit 'Sign in', :class => 'btn btn-inverse' %>
      <%= link_to "Forgot password?", new_password_path('user') %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
